                div(class='md:w-1/2')
                    label.block.text-sm.uppercase.text-gray-500.mb-5.font-bold(for="email") Precio
                        select(id="descripcion" class="w-full py-2 border px-3 block placeholder:italic" placeholder="Describe la propiedad a publicar" )
                            option(value="") - Seleccione - 
